title: [Regression] Color orange doesn't work.
description:
Description: The color orange is not displaying correctly. When attempting to set the color to orange, it does not appear as expected.
Steps to reproduce:
1. Insert a report item.
2. Set the color or background color to orange.
OB: The color orange does not display correctly when set as the color or background color.
EB: The color orange should display correctly when set as the color or background color.
SR:
1. Insert a report item.
2. Set the color or background color to orange.
